I grew up watching my father and admiring my grandfather's paintings on our walls. It gave me a clear sense of my path. After high school, I tried studying law and then administration, but something was missing.

Even before finishing college, I was freelancing in tattooing, photography, and illustration. In 2021, I had my first solo exhibition in Brasilia. The experience was incredible. On November 5th, 2021, I sold my first editions. This marked the beginning of my journey into the world of NFTs, web3.0, and the internet as a whole.
